  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To make an updated inventory of digital ulcer care protocols in scleroderma patients and to
      specify the French data on monthly healing rates and local care with patients in care centers
      experience, and thus to know the impact of ulcers in different dimensions To evaluate the
      rate of healed digital ulcers at the end of the study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
